							class="text-base-400 mt-2"
						>
							Use <code class="bg-base-800 rounded px-1"
								>base-*</code
							> for backgrounds, text, borders, and neutral UI elements.
							Lower numbers are lighter, higher numbers are darker.
						</Text>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
